    <h1> The Best Chocolate Chip Cookies</h1>
    <div>
      <img src="http://i.imgur.com/junuJG2.jpg" alt="cookies" />
    </div>
    <h2> Recipe by: Bonnie Owens</h2>
    <h3> RELATED RECIPES </h3>
